text: Emil Rothe (February 26, 1884 - February 24, 1966) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1966 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chicago
